  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What is v-on?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "The v-on directive is used to listen to DOM events and execute methods when those events are triggered."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Basic Syntax"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<button v-on:click=\"handleClick\">Click Me</button>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Shorthand Syntax"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<button @click=\"handleClick\">Click Me</button>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Inline Event Handling"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<button @click=\"count++\">Increment</button>\n<p>{{ count }}</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Passing Arguments"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<button @click=\"greet('John')\">Greet</button>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Event Object"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<button @click=\"handleClick($event)\">Click</button>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Event Modifiers"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "value": {
        "headers": ["Modifier", "Description"],
        "rows": [
          [".stop", "Stops event propagation"],
          [".prevent", "Prevents default action"],
          [".once", "Runs only once"],
          [".capture", "Uses capture mode"],
          [".self", "Triggers only on element itself"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Modifiers Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<form @submit.prevent=\"submitForm\">\n  <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n</form>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Keyboard Events"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<input @keyup.enter=\"submit\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use shorthand @ for cleaner code**",
        "**Keep logic inside methods**",
        "**Use modifiers to simplify event handling**",
        "**Avoid inline complex logic**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Mistakes"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Writing complex logic inline**",
